snippet.title: Moo Lander Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Moo Lander will be a 2D platformer game in which you fly on a spaceship, sucking cows, fighting enemies, solving puzzles and entering alien worlds.

Support the development of Moo Lander at http://moolander.com/ 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/moolander
Twitter: https://twitter.com/moolandergame
Instagram: http://instagram.com/moo.lander/
Website: http://moolander.com/
